Distribution . Known only from landings at Muttrah fish market (
Muscat
), indicating a local presence in the Gulf of Oman , Arabian Sea. Despite regular market and field surveys along the entire coast of Oman spanning almost 10 years, the species has not been recorded elsewhere. Similarly, the species has not been recorded from market surveys within the Persian Gulf (e.g.
Moore et al. , 2012
).
